gomodel:SYNGO_2407  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Inhibition of NECTIN1 by glycoprotein D increases synapse number in cultured rat hippocampal neurons.. Experimental description: Materials And Methods\nPrimary culture of rat hippocampal neurons.\nIn brief, hippocampi were isolated from rat embryos (20-d gestation), dissociated, plated on poly-l-lysine-coated glass coverslips, and cultured in MEM with 10% horse serum." ;
